

INSTALL

Installing this module (Lingua::EN::Bigram) should be trivial since it
requires no dependencies:

  $ perl Makefile.PL
  $ make
  $ make test
  $ make install

Once installed (or maybe even before) you should be able to see how it
works by:

  $ cd bin
  $ ./n-grams.pl ../etc/walden.txt

